<div class="title">A Bad Combination</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamine (Adderall) & Bupropion (Wellbutrin)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Rob&Exact=1">Rob</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Rob. "A Bad Combination: An Experience with Amphetamine (Adderall) & Bupropion (Wellbutrin) (exp8513)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Aug 2, 2001. erowid.org/exp/8513</div>

